title: GORGEOUS UNIT IN LUXURIOUS PARAMOUNT WORLD!!
posting_body: ['Welcome to an impeccable, fully furnished 1BD+Den condo with Miami skyline views!The unit features an expansive balcony/terrace, top of the line appliances and is located in one of the best buildings,Paramount Miami Worldcenter.', 'Be just minutes away from FTX Arena,Port of Miami,Philip & Patricia Frost Science Museum,Bayside Marketplace, Miami Beach,& a short drive to Miami International Airport.', 'PMWC is a resort-style building with 46 different amenities such as several pools, state of the art fitness centre, boxing ring, yoga studio, basketball and tennis courts, Spa, bbq kitchen, virtual golf, recording studio, racquetball, sunrise pool&children play area, skydeck observatory, & more', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
